# Lab 2 — same HTTP contract as lab1; manager mapped to host :8081 (8080 is for lab1).
# Run from this folder:  docker compose up --build
# Scale workers:  docker compose up --build --scale worker=3

### health
GET http://localhost:8081/

### crack "abcd" maxLength 4
POST http://localhost:8081/api/hash/crack
Content-Type: application/json

{"hash": "e2fc714c4727ee9395f324cd2e7f331f", "maxLength": 4}

### status (paste requestId)
GET http://localhost:8081/api/hash/status?requestId=ID

### metrics
GET http://localhost:8081/api/metrics

### list tasks
GET http://localhost:8081/api/hash/tasks
